WEBVTT
Kind: captions
Language: en

00:00:17.310 --> 00:00:19.790
KKBOX was founded in 2004

00:00:19.790 --> 00:00:21.740
We started off using cloud technology

00:00:21.740 --> 00:00:23.130
to provide a legally authorized

00:00:23.130 --> 00:00:25.190
music streaming service

00:00:27.570 --> 00:00:29.000
With the support of record companies,

00:00:29.000 --> 00:00:30.040
musicians

00:00:30.080 --> 00:00:32.400
and partners from the music industry

00:00:32.400 --> 00:00:34.350
We've become a mainstream music provider

00:00:34.350 --> 00:00:36.820
for online listeners

00:00:36.820 --> 00:00:39.690
We believe music makes our lives better

00:00:39.690 --> 00:00:41.090
That is why we strive to provide

00:00:41.090 --> 00:00:43.290
an even better music listening experience

00:00:43.290 --> 00:00:44.960
so that music can be affordable

00:00:44.960 --> 00:00:47.480
enjoyable and accessible

00:00:47.480 --> 00:00:49.870
at even more affordable prices

00:00:49.870 --> 00:00:52.560
and through various devices in your daily life

00:00:52.560 --> 00:00:55.370
to bring you the best music anytime, anywhere

00:00:57.070 --> 00:00:58.980
We use the Google Play platform

00:00:58.980 --> 00:01:00.810
to develop many new technologies

00:01:00.810 --> 00:01:03.220
and earned many accolades

00:01:03.220 --> 00:01:04.650
In 2015,

00:01:04.650 --> 00:01:07.120
we received Google Play "Best Apps of 2015" award

00:01:07.120 --> 00:01:08.540
In 2016,

00:01:08.540 --> 00:01:11.620
we received Google Play "Top Trending App"

00:01:11.620 --> 00:01:14.420
and "Most Entertaining App" awards

00:01:17.290 --> 00:01:19.110
Currently, over half of KKBOX active listeners

00:01:19.110 --> 00:01:21.600
are Android users

00:01:21.600 --> 00:01:22.620
Therefore Android has always been

00:01:22.620 --> 00:01:24.680
an important development focus for us

00:01:24.680 --> 00:01:27.510
Whether it’s Android TV, Chromecast

00:01:27.510 --> 00:01:29.310
or Android Auto

00:01:29.310 --> 00:01:31.080
or even the wearable Android Wear

00:01:31.080 --> 00:01:32.620
we are fully committed to product R&amp;D

00:01:32.620 --> 00:01:35.910
so that listeners can enjoy the best cross-platform music experience

00:01:35.910 --> 00:01:38.580
through these devices on our music service

00:01:41.022 --> 00:01:43.155
In May of 2016

00:01:43.150 --> 00:01:46.666
we started using Google Play In-app Billing.

00:01:46.660 --> 00:01:49.177
This payment method

00:01:49.170 --> 00:01:50.260
allows our members

00:01:50.260 --> 00:01:51.690
to complete the payment process

00:01:51.690 --> 00:01:53.300
in just a few simple steps

00:01:53.300 --> 00:01:55.711
Paired with customized messages

00:01:55.710 --> 00:01:58.355
it can effectively increase user’s willingness to buy

00:01:58.350 --> 00:02:00.622
Compared with other payment methods

00:02:00.620 --> 00:02:03.680
users can decide to make purchase quicker, 
taking approximately 50% less time.

00:02:03.680 --> 00:02:05.711
and it can also help speed up

00:02:05.710 --> 00:02:07.844
KKBOX buyer conversion

00:02:07.840 --> 00:02:10.840
We anticipate there will be more development in this area

00:02:12.222 --> 00:02:15.133
In 2009, we entered the international market

00:02:15.130 --> 00:02:16.933
by launching our services in Hong Kong

00:02:16.930 --> 00:02:19.933
Japan, and South East Asia

00:02:19.930 --> 00:02:21.244
Through IAB (Google Play In-app Billing)

00:02:21.240 --> 00:02:24.630
It has given us more flexibility

00:02:24.630 --> 00:02:27.590
in global commerce operations

00:02:29.644 --> 00:02:31.666
KKBOX will continue to enhance

00:02:31.660 --> 00:02:33.710
its products through content, features

00:02:33.710 --> 00:02:37.466
and platform technologies

00:02:39.266 --> 00:02:40.888
Our partnership with Google Play

00:02:40.880 --> 00:02:42.977
also enables us to provide advanced

00:02:42.970 --> 00:02:44.666
and convenient services

00:02:44.660 --> 00:02:47.800
to integrate with the entire music industry ecosystem

00:02:47.800 --> 00:02:50.200
so that we can provide a more exciting

00:02:50.200 --> 00:02:52.044
and richer experience

00:02:52.040 --> 00:02:54.550
to music lovers around the world

